    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Favored by soldiers deployed on airships, this chain mail has a built-in parachute connected to the armor itself, with an additional harness to be worn underneath. It takes 10 minutes and a successful DC 15 Crafting check to successfully repack the parachute.",
